{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead an expedition in this dice-based deckbuilding roguelike inspired by classic TRPGs. Roll the dice to attack enemies and counter their patterns. As you progress, recruit various companions and engage in tactical combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dice + Tactics</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battles take place on a 7x7 grid. Use dice rolls to move and attack with your heroes. Combine dice values to unleash powerful skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/MoveA.gif?t=1735010006\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>Strategically utilize enemy attacks and varied dice options to gain an advantage in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/CrossAttackA.gif?t=1735010006\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>16 Unique Heroes and Skill Combinations</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit a diverse cast of heroes as you progress and watch them grow stronger.  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/HeroChoiceA.gif?t=1735010006\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>Enhance heroes and dice to unlock a variety of skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/ChoiceA.gif?t=1735010006\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Procedurally Generated Worlds and Continuous Events</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience diverse encounters within a procedurally generated world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" s